{"code":200,"message":"","data":{"id":"306","movieId":"303","title":"大卫·艾克《雄狮醒来》","tag":"演讲·公开课","desc":"David Vaughan Icke，英国作家、公共演说家、前足球员与体育职业解说员。","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/christ-lion.jpg","introduces":[{"type":1000,"text":"David Vaughan Icke，英国作家、公共演说家、前足球员与体育职业解说员。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"他提出一种关于全球政治的阴谋论，并将它详细地写了出来。艾克曾是一名BBC电视台体育主持人和绿党的发言人。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/young-david-icke.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"1990年，一位通灵者告诉他，他是带着某种使命被派到地球上的“治愈者”，而且灵异世界将向他传达讯息。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"然而他继续发展他的想法，并且在七年内已经出版四本书。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/david-icke-img01.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"《机器的反抗》（The Robots\u0027 Rebellion，1994）、《真相使你自由》（And the Truth Shall Set You Free，1995）、《最大的秘密》（The Biggest Secret，1999）与《矩阵的孩子》（Children of the Matrix，2001）。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/david-icke-img02.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"在作品中，他把“新世纪理论”和现代社会极权化现象结合，提出一种世界性的观点。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/david-icke-img03.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"他的理论核心是一个由“爬虫类人”（包括乔治·W·布什、伊丽莎白二世、克里斯·克里斯托佛森及）组成的称为“巴比伦兄弟会”的秘密团体控制着人类，而且很多显赫的名流都是爬虫类人。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"他还宣称月球是一个人工建筑——“大概是个中空的行星”，在那里爬虫博克斯卡·威利类人给人类创造了一个“人工的自我意识和世界”，人类却误以为是真实。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/david-icke-img04.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"麦克·巴昆（Michael Barkun）把艾克的观点描述为“新世纪阴谋主义”，认为他是最有影响力的阴谋论流派。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"理查德·卡恩和泰森·刘易斯认为，爬虫类人的假设可能仅仅是斯威夫特式的讽刺，是一种让普通民众质疑他们身边所见事物的叙事方式。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/david-icke-img05.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"灵魂是用他的思想来染色。思考那些符合你的原则的事情，承担起生活赋予你的责任。你的品格取决于你的选择。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"日复一日，你选择什么、你思考什么、你做过什么你就会成为什么样的人。你的正直即是你的命运--那正是指引你的光芒。-- 大卫·艾克”","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"近年来，艾克更是频繁的到世界各地演讲。2011年，艾克开启了他的全球巡回演讲之旅。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"足迹遍及欧洲、美国、澳洲、新西兰、日本、以及南非。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/david-icke.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"目前国内出现了几部大卫艾克的带有中文字幕的演讲，包括《地球史上最震撼的访谈》、《超越世界》、《雄狮醒来》等。","image":""}],"videos":[{"id":"314","title":"1，实相的本质","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/christ-lion.jpg","playCount":"4","playNumber":1,"playNumberDesc":"第一集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d5039798\u0026cid\u003d8186325\u0026page\u003d1"},{"id":"315","title":"2，月球控制","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/christ-lion.jpg","playCount":"4","playNumber":2,"playNumberDesc":"第二集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d5039798\u0026cid\u003d8186325\u0026page\u003d2"},{"id":"316","title":"3，世界议程","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/christ-lion.jpg","playCount":"4","playNumber":3,"playNumberDesc":"第三集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d5039798\u0026cid\u003d8186325\u0026page\u003d3"},{"id":"317","title":"4，真相的共鸣","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/christ-lion.jpg","playCount":"4","playNumber":4,"playNumberDesc":"第四集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d5039798\u0026cid\u003d8186325\u0026page\u003d4"}]}}